  "text": "The relative coefficient of variation in percent (rel CV = CV/n 0.5 ! 100) was used to characterize the precision of repeated measurements. To compare the fluorescence intensity in samples treated with and without HCl, Student's test was used. RBBF values determined after simultaneous injection of FMs were compared using leastsquares linear regression and the method of Bland and Altman [CITATION_1] .",
